  "id": "RAW_58fa4f58",
  "title": "使用 Gemini 3 的谷歌搜索：迄今为止最智能的搜索",
  "url": "https://blog.google/products/search/gemini-3-search-ai-mode/",
  "date": "2025-11-18 16:27:26",
  "author": "Elizabeth Hamon Reid",
  "siteName": "The Keyword (blog.google) ",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <uni-article-speakable style=\"height: 55px; margin-bottom: 36px; display: block;\" page-title=\"Google Search with Gemini 3: Our most intelligent search yet\" listen-to-article=\"Listen to article\" data-date-modified=\"2025-11-18T16:27:26.904407+00:00\" data-tracking-ids=\"G-HGNBTNCHCQ,G-6NKTLKV14N\" data-voice-list=\"en.ioh-pngnat:Cyan,en.usb-pngnat:Lime\" data-script-src=\"https://www.gstatic.com/readaloud/player/web/api/js/api.js\" data-highlight-mode=\"word-over-paragraph\">\n   <!---->\n   <div id=\"uni-article-speakable\">\n    <!--?lit$329385562$-->\n    <span width=\"14px\"> \n     <svg width=\"24px\" viewBox=\"0 0 66 66\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" class=\"uni-spinner uni-spinner--small\">\n      <circle class=\"loader-path\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"7\" cx=\"33\" cy=\"33\" r=\"25\"></circle>\n     </svg> \n    </span>\n   </div>\n  </uni-article-speakable>\n  <!--article text-->\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Google Search with Gemini 3: Our most intelligent search yet&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <p data-block-key=\"3x5ev\" class=\"drop-cap\">Today, we <a href=\"https://blog.google/products/gemini/gemini-3\">introduced Gemini 3</a>, our most intelligent model with state-of-the-art reasoning, deep multimodal understanding and powerful agentic capabilities. It’s now available in Google Search, starting with <a href=\"http://google.com/ai\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">AI Mode</a> — marking the first time we’ve brought a Gemini model to Search on day one. Gemini 3 brings incredible reasoning power to Search because it’s built to grasp unprecedented depth and nuance for your hardest questions. It also unlocks new generative UI experiences so you can get dynamic visual layouts with interactive tools and simulations — generated specifically for you.</p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"1bk46\">Here’s how Gemini 3 is supercharging Search.</p>\n     <h2 data-block-key=\"faful\">Gemini 3: Our most intelligent model, right in Search</h2>\n     <p data-block-key=\"c7ejj\">Starting today, <a href=\"https://one.google.com/about/google-ai-plans/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Google AI Pro and Ultra subscribers</a> in the U.S. can use Gemini 3 Pro, our first model in the Gemini 3 family of models, by selecting “Thinking” from the model drop-down menu in AI Mode. With Gemini 3, you can tackle your toughest questions and learn more interactively because it better understands the intent and nuance of your request. And soon, we’ll bring Gemini 3 in AI Mode to everyone in the U.S. with higher limits for users with the Google AI Pro and Ultra plans.</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <uni-image-full-width alignment=\"full\" alt-text=\"AI Mode on the Search home page shows a user clicking on the new Thinking model from the AI Mode drop-down menu.\" external-image=\"\" or-mp4-video-title=\"Gemini 3 in AI Mode (Model Drop-down)\" or-mp4-video-url=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/Gemini_3_in_AI_Mode_Model_Drop-down.mp4\" section-header=\"Google Search with Gemini 3: Our most intelligent search yet\" custom-class=\"image-full-width--constrained-width uni-component-spacing\">\n   <!---->\n   <div class=\"image-full-width image-full-width--full image-full-width--constrained-width uni-component-spacing\" data-analytics-module=\"{&quot;module_name&quot;:&quot;Inline Images&quot;,&quot;section_header&quot;:&quot;Google Search with Gemini 3: Our most intelligent search yet&quot;}\">\n    <!--?lit$329385562$-->\n    <!--?lit$329385562$-->\n    <div class=\" image-full-width__media-asset image-full-width__media-asset--mp4 \">\n     <!--?lit$329385562$-->\n     <!--?lit$329385562$-->\n     <!--?lit$329385562$-->\n     <video autoplay=\"\" loop=\"\" muted playsinline=\"\" type=\"video/mp4\" aria-label=\"AI Mode on the Search home page shows a user clicking on the new Thinking model from the AI Mode drop-down menu.\" src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/Gemini_3_in_AI_Mode_Model_Drop-down.mp4\">\n      Sorry, your browser doesn't support embedded videos, but don't worry, you can <a href=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/Gemini_3_in_AI_Mode_Model_Drop-down.mp4\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">download it</a> and watch it with your favorite video player!\n     </video>\n     <!--?lit$329385562$-->\n     <!--?lit$329385562$-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?lit$329385562$-->\n     <!--?lit$329385562$-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?lit$329385562$-->\n     <!--?lit$329385562$-->\n     <!--?-->\n    </div>\n    <!--?-->\n    <!--?lit$329385562$-->\n    <!--?lit$329385562$-->\n    <!--?-->\n   </div>\n  </uni-image-full-width>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Google Search with Gemini 3: Our most intelligent search yet&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <p data-block-key=\"hbjch\">Thanks to Gemini 3’s advanced reasoning, Google Search’s <a href=\"https://search.google/pdf/google-about-AI-overviews-AI-Mode.pdf\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">query fan-out technique</a> is getting a major upgrade. Now, not only can it perform even <i>more</i> searches to uncover relevant web content, but because Gemini more <i>intelligently</i> understands your intent it can find new content that it may have previously missed. This means Search can help you find even more credible, highly relevant content for your specific question.</p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"brjoe\">And in the coming weeks, we’re also enhancing our automatic model selection in Search with Gemini 3. This means Search will intelligently route your most challenging questions in AI Mode and AI Overviews to this frontier model — while continuing to use faster models for simpler tasks. This will be rolling out to Google AI Pro and Ultra subscribers in the U.S.</p>\n     <h2 data-block-key=\"o6a5\">Generative UI: Visual layouts, interactive tools and simulations in AI Mode</h2>\n     <p data-block-key=\"4o56v\">Gemini 3’s unparalleled multimodal understanding and powerful agentic coding capabilities are also unlocking more bespoke generative user interfaces. Now, Gemini 3 in AI Mode can dynamically create the ideal visual layout for responses on the fly — featuring interactive tools and simulations — tailored to your query.</p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"7cnck\">To do this, Gemini 3 analyzes your question and creates the most helpful layout, building a custom response with visual elements — like images, tables and grids — so the final output isn’t just informative, but clear and actionable. When the model detects that an interactive tool will help you better understand the topic, it uses its generative capabilities to code a custom simulation or tool in real-time and adds it into your response.</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <uni-youtube-player-article index=\"4\" thumbnail-alt=\"A video shows an under-the-hood look at Gemini 3 in AI Mode, including helpful new generative UI experiences to code and create interactive tools and simulations on-the-fly, specific to your question.\" video-id=\"uYQGrK55gxQ\" video-type=\"video\">\n   <!---->\n   <div data-yt-video=\"module\" class=\"article-video-special h-c-page--mobile-full-bleed \" data-analytics-module=\"{&quot;module_name&quot;:&quot;Youtube Video&quot;}\">\n    <div class=\"article-video-special__container\">\n     <div class=\"article-module uni-article-video uni-article-video--body\" data-component=\"uni-article-yt-player\" data-page-title=\"\" data-video-id=\"uYQGrK55gxQ\" data-index-id=\"4\" data-type=\"video\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n      <button class=\"h-c-video h-c-video--marquee uni-article-video__custom-wrapper\" tabindex=\"0\">\n       <div class=\"uni-article-video__aspect-image\">\n        <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi_webp/uYQGrK55gxQ/default.webp\" alt=\"A video shows an under-the-hood look at Gemini 3 in AI Mode, including helpful new generative UI experiences to code and create interactive tools and simulations on-the-fly, specific to your question.\" data-loading=\"{\n                    &quot;desktop&quot;: &quot;https://i.ytimg.com/vi_webp/uYQGrK55gxQ/sddefault.webp&quot;,\n                    &quot;mobile&quot;: &quot;https://i.ytimg.com/vi_webp/uYQGrK55gxQ/mqdefault.webp&quot;\n                  }\"><uni-icon-component class=\"uni-article-video__icon-wrapper\" custom-class=\"uni-article-video__play-button--active\" remove-viewbox=\"true\" icon-id=\"yt_video_play_button_no_hole\"><!----></uni-icon-component><uni-icon-component class=\"uni-article-video__icon-wrapper\" custom-class=\"uni-article-video__play-button\" custom-role=\"img\" remove-viewbox=\"true\" icon-id=\"yt_video_play_button\" custom-label=\"Video Title \"><!----></uni-icon-component><!--?lit$329385562$-->\n        <div class=\"uni-article-video__duration loading\">\n         <uni-icon-component icon-id=\"yt_video_duration\" custom-class=\"uni-article-video__duration-icon\" remove-viewbox=\"true\"><!----></uni-icon-component><span class=\"uni-article-video__duration-time\">00:00</span>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </button>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </uni-youtube-player-article>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Google Search with Gemini 3: Our most intelligent search yet&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <p data-block-key=\"hbjch\">Say you’re learning about the physics behind the three-body problem. Instead of just reading about it, you can now get an interactive simulation, allowing you to manipulate variables and see the gravitational interactions play out. Or perhaps you're researching mortgage loans: Gemini 3 in AI Mode can make you a custom-built interactive loan calculator directly in the response so you can compare two different options and see which offers the most long-term savings. And to help you continue exploring, all responses have prominent links to high-quality content across the web.</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <uni-image-full-width alignment=\"full\" alt-text=\"Animation demonstrating AI Mode helping create a custom tool to help you explore complex physics topics like the 3 Body Problem\" external-image=\"\" or-mp4-video-title=\"Gemini 3 in AI Mode - Generative UI - 3 Body Problem\" or-mp4-video-url=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/Gemini_3_in_AI_Mode_Generative_UI_-_3_Body_Problem.mp4\" section-header=\"Google Search with Gemini 3: Our most intelligent search yet\" custom-class=\"image-full-width--constrained-width uni-component-spacing\">\n   <!---->\n   <div class=\"image-full-width image-full-width--full image-full-width--constrained-width uni-component-spacing\" data-analytics-module=\"{&quot;module_name&quot;:&quot;Inline Images&quot;,&quot;section_header&quot;:&quot;Google Search with Gemini 3: Our most intelligent search yet&quot;}\">\n    <!--?lit$329385562$-->\n    <!--?lit$329385562$-->\n    <div class=\" image-full-width__media-asset image-full-width__media-asset--mp4 \">\n     <!--?lit$329385562$-->\n     <!--?lit$329385562$-->\n     <!--?lit$329385562$-->\n     <video autoplay=\"\" loop=\"\" muted playsinline=\"\" type=\"video/mp4\" aria-label=\"Animation demonstrating AI Mode helping create a custom tool to help you explore complex physics topics like the 3 Body Problem\" src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/Gemini_3_in_AI_Mode_Generative_UI_-_3_Body_Problem.mp4\">\n      Sorry, your browser doesn't support embedded videos, but don't worry, you can <a href=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/Gemini_3_in_AI_Mode_Generative_UI_-_3_Body_Problem.mp4\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">download it</a> and watch it with your favorite video player!\n     </video>\n     <!--?lit$329385562$-->\n     <!--?lit$329385562$-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?lit$329385562$-->\n     <!--?lit$329385562$-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?lit$329385562$-->\n     <!--?lit$329385562$-->\n     <!--?-->\n    </div>\n    <!--?-->\n    <!--?lit$329385562$-->\n    <!--?lit$329385562$-->\n    <!--?-->\n   </div>\n  </uni-image-full-width>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Google Search with Gemini 3: Our most intelligent search yet&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <p data-block-key=\"hbjch\">For a deeper dive, check out <a href=\"https://research.google/blog/generative-ui-a-rich-custom-visual-interactive-user-experience-for-any-prompt/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Google’s foundational generative UI research</a>. We’ll continue to refine the experience over time, and we look forward to your feedback as you start to use these interactive tools and simulations in Search.</p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"2lfms\">Now, it's even easier to ask anything and instantly get a richer, more helpful understanding. We’re excited for you to try this more interactive and capable Search.<span class=\"tombstone\"></span></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <uni-related-content-tout title=\"Introducing Gemini 3\" cta=\"See more\" summary=\"Gemini 3, our most intelligent model, combines all of Gemini’s capabilities together so you can bring any idea to life.\" hideimage=\"False\" eyebrow=\"Collection\" image-alt-text=\"\" role=\"none\" fullurl=\"https://blog.google/products/gemini/gemini-3-collection/\" pagetype=\"collectiondetailpage\" isarticlepage=\"\">\n   <!---->\n   <section role=\"none\" class=\" related-content-tout related-content-tout--max-width uni-component-spacing \" data-analytics-module=\"{&quot;module_name&quot;:&quot;Related Content Tout&quot;,&quot;section_header&quot;:&quot;Introducing Gemini 3&quot;}\">\n    <a class=\"related-content-tout__wrapper\" href=\"https://blog.google/products/gemini/gemini-3-collection/\" aria-label=\"\n      Collection.\n       Introducing Gemini 3.\n      Gemini 3, our most intelligent model, combines all of Gemini’s capabilities together so you can bring any idea to life. See more\"><!--?lit$329385562$--></a>\n   </section>\n  </uni-related-content-tout>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "谷歌搜索集成 Gemini 3，提供先进的推理能力、多模态理解和生成式用户界面，以及互动工具和模拟，带来更智能、更个性化的搜索体验。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "谷歌搜索集成 Gemini 3，提供先进的推理能力、多模态理解和生成式用户界面，以及互动工具和模拟，带来更智能、更个性化的搜索体验。",
  "summary": "本文宣布将谷歌最智能的 AI 模型 Gemini 3 集成到谷歌搜索中，特别是在“AI 模式 (AI Mode)”中。 这种集成将最先进的推理能力、深入的多模态理解和强大的 Agent 能力带到搜索查询中。 关键增强功能包括升级的查询扩展技术，用于更智能的内容发现；以及自动模型选择，将复杂问题导向 Gemini 3 处理。 一项重大创新是引入生成式用户界面，可以根据用户查询定制可视化布局、互动工具和模拟，例如互动式三体问题模拟器或定制的抵押贷款计算器。 这些功能最初提供给美国的 Google AI Pro 和 Ultra 订阅者，旨在提供更丰富、更有帮助和更具互动性的搜索体验，为信息检索和用户互动设定新标准。",
